{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/getCurrentPosition","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Geolocation_API\">Geolocation API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Geolocation\"><code>Geolocation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/clearWatch\"><code>clearWatch()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>getCurrentPosition()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/watchPosition\"><code>watchPosition()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Geolocation API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates\"><code>GeolocationCoordinates</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition\"><code>GeolocationPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError\"><code>GeolocationPositionError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/geolocation\"><code>Navigator.geolocation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Secure context:</strong> This feature is available only in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">secure contexts (en-US)</a> (HTTPS), in some or all <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">supporting browsers</a>.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Mit der Methode <strong><code>Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()</code></strong> kann die Position des Gerätes bestimmt werden.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(<var>success</var>[, <var>error</var>[, [<var>options</var>]])</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"success\"><code><var>success</var></code></dt>\n <dd>Eine Funktion, die nach erfolgreicher Positionsbestimmung aufgerufen wird. Sie erhält ein Objekt vom Typ <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition\"><code>GeolocationPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> als Parameter.</dd>\n <dt id=\"error\"><code><var>error</var></code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>Eine Funktion, die im Fehlerfall aufgerufen wird. Sie erhält ein Objekt vom Typ <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError\"><code>GeolocationPositionError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> als Parameter.</dd>\n <dt id=\"options\"><code><var>options</var></code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>Ein Objekt vom Typ <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/getCurrentPosition\"><code>PositionOptions</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Es enthält:\n <ul>\n  <li><code>maximumAge</code>: Die Positionsbestimmung darf höchstens diese Zeit in Millisekunden zurückliegen. Falls 0, muss ein aktueller Wert ermittelt werden, falls&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Infinity\">Infinity</a></code>, sollte kein aktueller Wert ermittelt werden.<br>\n   Vorgabe: 0.</li>\n  <li><code>timeout</code>: Wartezeit in Millisekunden, bis die Positionsbestimmung abgebrochen und, so gegeben, die Funktion <code>error</code> aufgerufen wird. Bei&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Infinity\">Infinity</a></code> keine Begrenzung.<br>\n   Vorgabe: <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Infinity\">Infinity</a></code>.</li>\n  <li><code>enableHighAccuracy</code>: <code>true</code>, um eine genauere Position zu ermitteln, jedoch möglicherweise zu Lasten von Wartezeit und Energieverbrauch.<br>\n   Vorgabe: <code>false</code>.</li>\n </ul>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> options <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">enableHighAccuracy</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">timeout</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">5000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">maximumAge</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">success</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">pos</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> crd <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pos<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>coords<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Your current position is:'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Latitude : </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>crd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>latitude<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Longitude: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>crd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>longitude<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">More or less </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>crd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>accuracy<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\"> meters.</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">err</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">warn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">ERROR(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>err<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>code<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">): </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>err<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>message<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nnavigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>geolocation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getCurrentPosition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>success<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> error<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/geolocation-api/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'Geolocation API' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">Geolocation API</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Erste Spezifikation.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.Geolocation.getCurrentPosition","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/getCurrentPosition/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Geolocation_API/Using_the_Geolocation_API\">Die Benutzung der Geolocation-API</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/geolocation\"><code>Navigator.geolocation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Mit der Methode Geolocation.getCurrentPosition() kann die Position des Gerätes bestimmt werden.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/geolocation/getcurrentposition","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/geolocation/getcurrentposition/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Geolocation","title":"Geolocation"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/getCurrentPosition","title":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()"}],"pageTitle":"Geolocation.getCurrentPosition() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}